  Q. How does this course compare to Abu Dhabi?   
 SERGIO GARCÃA: I'd say it's playing harder, mainly use it's usually windier here. But I think the firmness of the greens here is usually greater than Abu Dhabi. The greens, even though we have good weather in Abu Dhabi, the greens are grainier and because of that, it's harder to make them true. So this week, I think it's definitely a little bit tougher.   
  
