  Q. You mentioned the wind?  
 SERGIO GARCÃA: Yes, it can get very windy here. It's supposed to be windy on Friday. It's the type of course that you have to be very patient when the week comes around, because some holes are playing very soft and then you're going to have some birdie holes. And with the way the greens are at the moment, being quite firm and a good speed, it will be a very good test.   
  
